## 基本測試
```go
// math.go
package math

func Add(a, b int) int {
    return a + b
}

// math_test.go
package math

import "testing"

func TestAdd(t *testing.T) {
    result := Add(2, 3)
    if result != 5 {
        t.Errorf("Add(2,3) = %d; want 5", result)
    }
}
```

執行：
```bash
go test                # 當前 package
go test ./...          # 所有
go test -v             # 詳細
go test -race          # 偵測 race condition
go test -cover         # 看覆蓋率
```

## Table-Driven Tests（Go 風格）
```go
func TestAdd(t *testing.T) {
    tests := []struct {
        name     string
        a, b     int
        expected int
    }{
        {"positive", 2, 3, 5},
        {"negative", -1, -1, -2},
        {"zero", 0, 5, 5},
    }

    for _, tt := range tests {
        t.Run(tt.name, func(t *testing.T) {
            got := Add(tt.a, tt.b)
            if got != tt.expected {
                t.Errorf("got %d, want %d", got, tt.expected)
            }
        })
    }
}
```

## Benchmark
```go
func BenchmarkAdd(b *testing.B) {
    for i := 0; i < b.N; i++ {
        Add(2, 3)
    }
}
```

```bash
go test -bench=.
# BenchmarkAdd-8   1000000000   0.30 ns/op
```

## Subtests + parallel
```go
func TestAdd(t *testing.T) {
    t.Run("test 1", func(t *testing.T) {
        t.Parallel()
        // ...
    })
}
```

## Mock / Stub
Go 通常用 interface + 手寫 mock（不用大型 mock 套件）：
```go
type UserRepo interface {
    GetByID(id string) (*User, error)
}

type mockUserRepo struct{}

func (m *mockUserRepo) GetByID(id string) (*User, error) {
    return &User{Name: "Mock"}, nil
}

// 測試用 mockUserRepo
```

## testify（推薦套件）
```bash
go get github.com/stretchr/testify
```
```go
import (
    "testing"
    "github.com/stretchr/testify/assert"
    "github.com/stretchr/testify/require"
)

func TestUser(t *testing.T) {
    user := getUser()
    assert.Equal(t, "Alice", user.Name)
    assert.NotNil(t, user.Email)
    require.NoError(t, user.Save())  // 失敗就停
}
```

## httptest（測 HTTP handler）
```go
import "net/http/httptest"

func TestHandler(t *testing.T) {
    req := httptest.NewRequest("GET", "/users/1", nil)
    w := httptest.NewRecorder()

    myHandler(w, req)

    if w.Code != 200 {
        t.Errorf("expected 200, got %d", w.Code)
    }
}
```

